@host = http://localhost:5000

### Root
GET {{host}}/

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Servers
GET {{host}}/api/servers

### Server detail
GET {{host}}/api/servers/1

### Update server status
POST {{host}}/api/servers/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": 1,
  "lastCheckedAt": "2026-07-02T12:00:00Z",
  "failureCount": 0,
  "message": "TCP port is reachable"
}

### Server history
GET {{host}}/api/servers/1/history